# Razorpay — storefront (safe in browser)
# 1) https://dashboard.razorpay.com → Account & Settings → API Keys
# 2) Copy Key Id (rzp_test_… or rzp_live_…). Never put Key Secret in VITE_*.
VITE_RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=

# Razorpay — server only (Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables)
# RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=
# RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=

# ─── Resend (order emails) — https://resend.com ───────────────────────────────
# 1) Sign up → API Keys → create key → RESEND_API_KEY=re_...
# 2) Domains → add your domain OR for testing use onboarding@resend.dev (sends only to your Resend account email until domain is verified)
# 3) RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=Shivaanya Collection <orders@yourdomain.com>
#    or: orders@yourdomain.com  (display name added automatically)
# 4) ORDER_NOTIFY_EMAIL=anjalikumari.shivcollection@gmail.com  (you get an email on every new order)

# RESEND_API_KEY=
# RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=Shivaanya Collection <orders@yourdomain.com>
# ORDER_NOTIFY_EMAIL=anjalikumari.shivcollection@gmail.com
# ORDER_SITE_URL=https://shivaanya-collection-shivaanya.vercel.app

# ─── Twilio (order SMS) — https://console.twilio.com ──────────────────────────
# Customer SMS: sent to the mobile number entered at checkout.
# Company SMS: optional alert to your phone when a new order arrives.
#
# 1) Create account → get Account SID + Auth Token
# 2) Phone Numbers → buy a number with SMS (or use Messaging Service)
# 3) TWILIO_SMS_FROM=+1xxxxxxxxxx  (your Twilio number, E.164)
# 4) TWILIO_NOTIFY_PHONE=+918439192467  (optional — your shop mobile for new-order alerts)
#
# India note: SMS to Indian numbers (+91) requires DLT template registration on Twilio.
# Register a transactional template (order confirmation) in Twilio Console → Messaging → Regulatory Compliance.

# TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=
# TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=
# TWILIO_SMS_FROM=
# TWILIO_NOTIFY_PHONE=+918439192467

# ─── Google Sheet (orders log) ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Sheet: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1BzA3Lq9mLGFD21TI_sk04mc8TJ_ITEhsb9YMInTChQ/edit
# Paste scripts/google-sheets-order-webhook.gs → Deploy as Web app → set URL + secret below

# GOOGLE_SHEETS_WEBHOOK_URL=https://script.google.com/macros/s/.../exec
# GOOGLE_SHEETS_WEBHOOK_SECRET=your-long-random-secret

VITE_MEDIA_BASE_URL=https://shivaanya-collection-media.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com
